Invigilators/Examiner
- ,
Ref. JB3045411
Job Description
We are currently looking for invigilators/examiners for students who will pursue their exams in May 2014 for a reputed university in Abu Dhabi, UAE.
Part time position only
English, Arabic & french knowledge is a must
We will be paying the invigilators AED 80/- per hour.
Skills
Dates required: May 11th - 15th and 18th-20th.
We also have upcoming exams in June & July for the same.
Any gender/nationality.
If interested with knowledge in Arabic, French & English, please send your CV immediately to serena(at)reachgroup(dot)ae
